window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>When one needy boy makes taking it slow impossible...</b></p> <p>Sivney is determined to take his sweet time to get to know his new lovers, Naran and Lev. After all, they each brought quite a bit of baggage into their relationship, and figuring out how they fit together is not easy. </p> <p>But Lev can’t wait until Sivney is ready for more. He needs Sivney and Naran to take care of him <i>now</i>. Preferably, like, yesterday. Will Sivney step up when Lev needs more than he’s willing to give initially?</p> <p>The pack as a whole has bigger worries. Civil war is on the verge of breaking out, and since the capital is only miles away, that doesn’t bode well for the pack members. But when one of the pack members becomes deadly sick, even war isn’t their first concern anymore....</p> <p><i>Omega’s Power </i>is book eight in the Irresistible Omegas series, a best-selling mpreg romance series that needs to be listened to in order to enjoy the plot lines fully. This MMM romance has a little kink, a lot of love, and some high-angst moments but ends with a HEA for all characters.</p>"; 
